ED_Title: Proposed programme of work and timetable of the Special Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee) for the eighty-first session of the General Assembly
ED_DecisionText: At its 55th plenary meeting, on 5 December 2025, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the Special Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee),  (Footnote: A/80/537, para. 16, Draft decision 6.) approved the proposed programme of work and timetable of the Special Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee) for the eighty-first session of the Assembly as set out in the report of the Committee (A/80/537).
ED_Disclaimer: The final text of this decision will be contained in document A/80/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
